OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781305387
OL,3,CDisqualified director jailed for #3
OL,4,Cmillion fraud
OL,6,FTim Scott was in Manchester Crown
OL,7,FCourt for the sentencing of Tariq
OL,8,FSarwar (pictured).
OL,10,FThe two men were sentenced at
OL,11,FManchester Crown Court for a multi-
OL,12,Fmillion pound insolvency fraud and
OL,13,Fmoney laundering conspiracy which
OL,14,Fbankrolled their lavish lifestyle.
OL,16,FThe court heard Tariq Sarwar
OL,17,Ffraudulently transferred more than #3
OL,18,Fmillion from the sale of a Salford
OL,19,Fcommercial property.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
