FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781305387
OL,3,CDisqualified director jailed for #3
OL,4,Cmillion fraud
OL,6,FChristopher Francis laundered the
OL,7,Fmoney through a network of accounts
OL,8,Fand companies, returning funds to
OL,9,FSarwar with creditors losing out.
OL,11,FThe Insolvency Service said 59-year-
OL,12,Fold disqualified director Tariq Sarwar
OL,13,Fknew his company was in financial
OL,14,Fdifficulty and likely to be wound up
OL,15,Fwhen he sold commercial property in
OL,16,FSalford ` his company's only
OL,17,Fsubstantial asset - for more than #5
OL,18,Fmillion.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781305387
OL,3,CDisqualified director jailed for #3
OL,4,Cmillion fraud
OL,6,FSarwar fraudulently transferred more
OL,7,Fthan #3 million from the proceeds of
OL,8,Fthat sale without paying off his
OL,9,Fcompany's debts to HM Revenue and
OL,10,FCustoms (HMRC) and other creditors.
OL,12,FThe money went to a food and drinks
OL,13,Fcompany controlled by 40-year-old
OL,14,FChristopher Francis, who laundered the
OL,15,Ffunds through a network of accounts
OL,16,Fand other companies back to Sarwar.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
