OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781305387
OL,3,CDisqualified director jailed for #3
OL,4,Cmillion fraud
OL,6,FWhile creditors were left owed more
OL,7,Fthan #500,000, Sarwar and his family
OL,8,Fenjoyed a lavish lifestyle in the
OL,9,FCheshire countryside, including a six-
OL,10,Fbedroom home filled with designer
OL,11,Fproducts from Versace and Louis
OL,12,FVuitton.
OL,14,FHis son even appeared on reality
OL,15,Ftelevision programme Rich Kids Go
OL,16,FSkint, filmed in the summer of 2019,
OL,17,Fwhere he admitted he had never been on
OL,18,Fa bus before and was chauffeured
OL,19,Faround in a Rolls-Royce.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781305387
OL,3,CDisqualified director jailed for #3
OL,4,Cmillion fraud
OL,6,FSarwar, of Gore Lane, Alderley Edge,
OL,7,Fadmitted charges of fraudulently
OL,8,Fremoving assets in anticipation of
OL,9,Fwinding-up and acting as a company
OL,10,Fdirector while disqualified in April
OL,11,Fthis year.
OL,13,FHe was jailed for four years and
OL,14,Fbanned as a company director for 10
OL,15,Fyears when he appeared at Manchester
OL,16,FCrown Court on 12 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
