OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781305387
OL,3,CDisqualified director jailed for #3
OL,4,Cmillion fraud
OL,6,FFrancis, of Letchworth Road, Luton,
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty in the middle of his
OL,8,Ftrial last month to one count of money
OL,9,Flaundering under the Proceeds of Crime
OL,10,FAct 2002.
OL,12,FHe was sentenced to two years and one
OL,13,Fmonth in prison, suspended for two
OL,14,Fyears, at the same hearing.
OL,16,FFrancis was also ordered to carry out
OL,17,F250 hours of unpaid work.
OL,19,FThe Insolvency Service has already
OL,20,Fstarted investigations to confiscate
OL,21,Fthe funds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781305387
OL,3,CDisqualified director jailed for #3
OL,4,Cmillion fraud
OL,6,FMeanwhile, David Snasdell, Chief
OL,7,FInvestigator at the Insolvency
OL,8,FService, said:
OL,10,F"Tariq Sarwar and Christopher Francis
OL,11,Fwent to considerable lengths to hide
OL,12,Ftheir criminal actions, moving
OL,13,Fmillions of pounds through a web of
OL,14,Fcompanies to cover their tracks.
OL,16,F"Property companies do not hand more
OL,17,Fthan #3 million to an unconnected food
OL,18,Fand drinks business out of generosity.
OL,19,FThis was fraud, plain and simple.
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
